  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You talked about your memories now and looking back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, with my wife now, as I said, my first wife was born in the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was very little-- they didn't-- weren't aware of what was going on 'til we got married.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mean, they knew some of it, but-- But Sylvia had a similar experience as mine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was born in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her father was in the-- the highest official in the Polish government.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] five minutes before the German Army came into Warsaw, literally, he commandeered a car and chauffeur, which he was able to get, and said to-- to Sylvia and her mother, I'll be going into the-- he had written a book about Germany in 1933, so he was on the list.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was on Hitler's black list and-- what was happening in Germany in '36, whenever he wrote.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so he had to flee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, I'll go into the-- into the woods, into the forest, in the countryside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when this thing is over, we'll-- I'll come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And not expecting-- A, expecting the British to come in, as almost everybody did at that moment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The French and the British would prevent Hitler from marching into-- into taking over Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And B, also that if they were there, the Germans, they wouldn't kill people, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They wouldn't kill civilians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so the chauffeur said to him, no, I think you're much better off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Take your family too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so they packed a suitcase in 20 minutes, and they left, and eventually, after all kinds of harrowing experiences, wound up in Vilna, Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
